            <lg xml:id="TK649">
<l>palacollak kāmuṟuvar maṉṟamā caṟṟa</l>
<l>cilacolla ṟēṟṟā tavar</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>They will desire to utter many words, who do not know how to speak a few faultless ones.</l>
